div.tsd-comment.tsd-typography.p: Attaches a callback for only the rejection of the Promise.

div.tsd-description.p: A Promise for the completion of the callback.

div.tsd-comment.tsd-typography.p:
Attaches a callback that is invoked when the Promise is settled (fulfilled or rejected). The
resolved value cannot be modified from the callback.

div.tsd-description.p: A Promise for the completion of the callback.

div.tsd-comment.tsd-typography.p: Attaches callbacks for the resolution and/or rejection of the Promise.

div.tsd-description.p: A Promise for the completion of which ever callback is executed.
